    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>Some readers scrutinized our article on political comedy -- and counted campaign buttons on the cover -- for signs of liberal bias; others invented their own one-liners. Many found the officers' isolation at the root of the L.A.P.D. scandal. And ''flying waitresses'' plotted revenge.</p>
